documentation to show that bush and quayle share a common ancestor 
with monroes supposed father charles stanley gifford who was born 
in rhode island in 1888 and died in california in 1965 
most monroe biographies cite gifford as the man monroes mother 
claimed was her father monroes mother never married gifford but 
monroe and gifford made contact with each other over the years 
