one of the conditions for us recognition of the plo 
previously the plo had explicitly rejected resolution 242 which 
calls for israels withdrawal from territories occupied in 1967 and 
for the right of all states in the region to live in peace within 
secure and recognized borders an implicit recognition of israel 
