stand an indiana supreme court decision that a husband has no right 
to interfere with his wifes constitutional right to abort her 
pregnancy the state courts ruling last july was based directly on 
past rulings by the nations highest court 
the case is conn vs conn 88347 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
the court denied an emergency request from deposed philippine 
president ferdinand marcos and his wife imelda that they not be 
compelled to abide by a federal grand jurys request for financial 
and other records related to an investigation of the couple a 
federal judge in new york ruled aug 11 that the marcoses who are 
charged with looting their nations treasury of more than 100 
million must honor the subpoenas and no longer have immunity as 
ruler and first lady of a foreign country 
the case is marcos vs us a361 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
