chief whom they accused of corruption and inaction they turned 
back only after a high party official was sent out to the highway to 
meet with them 
armenia by all accounts will never be the same 
these past 10 months have been like a century stamboltsyan 
said we have learned so much its as if the entire republic has 
been to university 
